refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     7.3.0

      This function can now be called with only one parameter. Formerly, at
      least two parameters have been required.

  &reftitle.examples;



    array_push example


<?php
$stack = array("orange", "banana");
array_push($stack, "apple", "raspberry");
print_r($stack);
?>


    &example.outputs;


Array
(
    [0] => orange
    [1] => banana
    [2] => apple
    [3] => raspberry
)
